Process called "uint32_unpack_be" takes buffer as Integer returns Integer:
    Let b0 be Memory.memory_get_byte(buffer, 0)
    Let b1 be Memory.memory_get_byte(buffer, 1)
    Let b2 be Memory.memory_get_byte(buffer, 2)
    Let b3 be Memory.memory_get_byte(buffer, 3)
    Return Bitwise.bitwise_or(Bitwise.left_shift(b0, 24), Bitwise.bitwise_or(Bitwise.left_shift(b1, 16), Bitwise.bitwise_or(Bitwise.left_shift(b2, 8), b3)))
